{"tid":1083204,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"男子上班期間即興到淺水灣行山　失足墮坡受傷","createTime":"2019-03-29T12:39:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-29T16:58:04.000Z","uid":122,"like":33,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"b0b0682dc5d05e01a9b931e8217434d8ecd6ab7a","tid":1083204,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T12:39:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20190329/s00001/d4817857d0a655e377ee18a14f2416af.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20190329%2Fs00001%2Fd4817857d0a655e377ee18a14f2416af.jpg&h=6313e33e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【16:14更新】現場消息稱，男事主43歲，居於慈雲山。今早他於柴灣康翠臺附近上班期間，突即興駕車到南灣坊行山，隨後他看見一道石牆，欲爬上石牆，未料失足墮坡受傷。<br />\n<br />\n【16:00】淺水灣一名男子墮坡受傷，由直升機送院治理。現場為南灣坊。下午1時33分，警方接獲一名男子報案，表示獨自於上址行山期間，誤踩石頭失足，跌落10米山坡下。男子腰背部受傷清醒，惟無法移動。消防及飛行服務隊到場展開救援。傷者由直升機吊起，送往東區醫院治理。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d505f6804013062b665fd1dab6412bf33c7ed1c5","tid":1083204,"uid":30049,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T12:40:25.000Z","msg":"自己都覺得柒到冇眼睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"608e82d6b7b4c15e35109b8951cd177dfe4eac44","tid":1083204,"uid":103936,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T12:41:53.000Z","msg":"唔知事主返咩工呢"},{"pid":"e9028fdaae3326089be45c7ba627a74f438b25fe","tid":1083204,"uid":119610,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T12:42:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VxcLKJL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVxcLKJL.png&h=c75704b8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"700900105cfffa0fd72210be844dc2e36ca469a0","tid":1083204,"uid":64694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T12:42:50.000Z","msg":"即興<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 本來idea幾好，但係受傷就真係柒咗啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e52c31a48b17d04f5e069a3ffdd6fc9a4391ed5","tid":1083204,"uid":26506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T12:43:33.000Z","msg":"Link?"},{"pid":"a52eb912db7761eabf453dadab81a2d322fea850","tid":1083204,"uid":56999,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T12:44:25.000Z","msg":"返工期間受傷<br />\n快d報工傷"},{"pid":"9dcf6ec29b8732ca9e842ef4d79dde573c860f54","tid":1083204,"uid":162539,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T12:44:45.000Z","msg":"一定係睇左呢個post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1071302\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1071302</a>"},{"pid":"3014c0dc144365d76bb0d7eada8cfc4b4a0f6795","tid":1083204,"uid":149566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T12:46:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />遮住個樣就啱啦<br />\n比人笑一世就唔好啦"},{"pid":"3dcbdf4db952d2fa6b1fb1664e1baad120b9eb6c","tid":1083204,"uid":103156,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T12:52:17.000Z","msg":"踩線？"},{"pid":"fcf112b90dc35e5ed49d3eaeb6075a63d5f5811e","tid":1083204,"uid":63154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T13:23:59.000Z","msg":"人地唔想返工，連登仔唔係應該欣賞咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d7a014cd409a4c4e65221345b52ac2304b16a24","tid":1083204,"uid":211461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T14:28:14.0